{"tid":1525953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［機場攻略］你知道嗎？T1落客區除咗入客運大樓就只有一個途徑離場","createTime":"2019-09-01T03:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T02:43:18.000Z","uid":23707,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8f8e0072b04a23497ce1f750ee4afb2cc082af6c","tid":1525953,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:42:56.000Z","msg":"其實第一日封機場，機管局係忽略咗呢個問題<br />\n喺T1如果佢唔比市民入去客運大樓<br />\n其實係無路走嘅<br />\n所以第日開始佢哋搵咗城巴租車<br />\n由T1去T2載走啲唔入得客運大樓嘅人<br />\n呢個係唯一途徑<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當然啦如果人少少緊係疏散得切啲人<br />\n但係如果人太多就一定散唔切<br />\n成個T1落客區都會係等車走嘅人</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴日所見城巴應該只係派咗3-4架車<br />\n如果人太多車唔夠 真係想塞爆個落客區咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋路程咁短<br />\n大家唔好專登走上上層坐咁多餘喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DCOUDx2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDCOUDx2.png&h=20adf2b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4gUAnZO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4gUAnZO.png&h=82286f36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aDOabTf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaDOabTf.png&h=7b4025d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下巴士線係喺T1離港層落客區停站嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部A線<br />\n龍運E33 E33P E34A E34B E41<br />\n其他E線同S線全部唔到<br />\n大家唔好搭錯車呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5ec7a3283215150d76ec2bba97c93808e4287d","tid":1525953,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:44:38.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"6eba46bbd33a595a137b262e6ad64754f708ccb4","tid":1525953,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:46:23.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"6ae4752f2e9393cb7aa35fd8bdc27e606